OL,3,CHow much are the US and its allies
OL,4,Cspending on weapons in the Iran war?
OL,6,FWhen three US F-15 fighter jets were
OL,7,Fdowned by friendly fire on Monday, the
OL,8,Fpilots ejected safely, meaning there
OL,9,Fwas no human cost - but there was an
OL,10,Feconomic one.
OL,12,FEach plane cost #23 million - that's a
OL,13,Fcombined #69 million of military
OL,14,Fhardware damaged or destroyed.
OL,16,FFor that price, Iran could build 2,600
OL,17,FShahed drones - their current mainline
OL,18,Fweapon of choice.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
