OL,3,CHow much are the US and its allies
OL,4,Cspending on weapons in the Iran war?
OL,6,FUp to 3.5 metres long, they can carry
OL,7,Fa 40kg payload for 1,500 miles at
OL,8,F115mph.
OL,10,FIn the first four days of the
OL,11,Fconflict, the UAE claims to have shot
OL,12,Fdown 755 of the 812 drones sent to
OL,13,Fattack them. An impressive intercept
OL,14,Frate of 93% - but at what cost?
OL,16,FEach drone costs #26,000 - so Iran
OL,17,Fspent #21m on the 812 dispatched.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
