OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1772647565
OL,3,CHow much are the US and its allies
OL,4,Cspending on weapons in the Iran war?
OL,6,FInterceptor missiles are estimated to
OL,7,Fcost between #370,000 and #1 million
OL,8,Feach. Multiply that by the 755
OL,9,Fsuccessful takedowns, and you're
OL,10,Flooking at between #280 million and
OL,11,F#755 million spent by the UAE.
OL,13,FCheaper than repairing potential
OL,14,Fdamage but between 13 and 33 times
OL,15,Fmore than Iran spent to attack.
OL,17,FPlus, as American Secretary of State
OL,18,FMarco Rubio admitted, it is much
OL,19,Fquicker to rebuild and restock drones
OL,20,Fand missiles than it is to
OL,21,Finterceptors.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
