OL,3,CHow much are the US and its allies
OL,4,Cspending on weapons in the Iran war?
OL,6,FHe told reporters that Iran is capable
OL,7,Fof producing 100 missiles and
OL,8,Fthousands of attack drones a month,
OL,9,Fwhereas only six or seven interceptors
OL,10,Fcan be manufactured in the same period.
OL,12,FThe real fear is that you waste your
OL,13,Fdefensive armoury fighting off cheap
OL,14,Fweapons and then are defenceless
OL,15,Fagainst the bigger missiles later on.
OL,17,FIt's a lesson learned in Ukraine.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
