OL,11,FQuadcopter interceptor drones, which
OL,12,Fcan be manufactured for about #2,000,
OL,13,Fare now being used.
OL,15,FPresident Zelenskyy put out a
OL,16,Fstatement on social media saying: "We
OL,17,Fare ready to share this experience and
OL,18,Fhelp those nations that helped
OL,19,FUkraine."
