OL,3,CHow much are the US and its allies
OL,4,Cspending on weapons in the Iran war?
OL,6,FIsrael is trying out laser defences `
OL,7,FIron Beam can shoot down drones and
OL,8,Fmissiles at a range of 10km for just a
OL,9,Fcouple of pounds a shot. But there are
OL,10,Frumours that its effectiveness is
OL,11,Flimited in bad weather.
OL,13,FAmerica and Israel's tactics seem to
OL,14,Fbe to hit the launchers and guidance
OL,15,Fsystems Iran needs to launch attacks.
OL,16,FTheir military leaders will hope they
OL,17,Fdestroy those before their own
OL,18,Fdefences get overstretched.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
